  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.10">
<l>mañculāñ cōlai vaṇṭaṟai mānīr</l>
<l>maṅkaiyār vāḷkali kaṉṟi</l>
<l>ceñcolā leṭutta teyvanaṉ mālai</l>
<l>yivaikoṇṭu cikkeṉat toṇṭīr.</l>
<l>tuñcumpēā taḻaimiṉ tuyarvaril niṉaimiṉ</l>
<l>tuyarilīr collilum naṉṟām</l>
<l>nañcutāṉ kaṇṭīr nammuṭai viṉaikku</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are servants, firmly grasping these [verses in]</l>
<l rend="indent">the excellent divine garland uttered with fine words</l>
<l>By Kalikaṉṟi, sword[-bearer] of the people of well-watered Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">where bees hum in groves where mist drifts,</l>
<l>Shout [them] when you languish; think of [them], if misery arises.</l>
<l rend="indent">Even if you who are without misery say it, it is good.</l>
<l>See [how it is like] poison to our karma,</l>
<l rend="indent">the name which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
